<tool id="show_image_information" name="Show" version="0.0.1">
  <description> image information </description>
  <command interpreter="bash">
    show_image_information.sh $dataset
  </command>
  <inputs>
    <param name="dataset" type="data" format="tif" label="Choose an image" multiple="false" optional="false" />
  </inputs>
  <outputs>
    <data format="html" name="output" from_work_dir="index.html"/>
  </outputs>
<help>

**Description**

Shows information about a given image. 

-----

**Input**

An OME.TIFF file.

-----

**Output**

A valid html file.

</help>
</tool>
